ROWS.heading: Contact Information
ROWS.subheading: Your contact information will be used for account-related communications and to keep you informed about updates and important notifications. We value your privacy and will not share your contact details with third parties without your consent.

ROWS.heading: Identification
ROWS.subheading: Your identification details are required for secure account creation and to ensure that your profile is unique and verifiable.

ROWS.heading: Professional Details
ROWS.subheading: Your professional details help us tailor the content and services to match your career interests and networking needs.

ROWS.heading: Social Media Presence
ROWS.subheading: Sharing your social media profiles allows us to enhance your networking opportunities and integrate your online presence with our platform.

ROWS.heading: Address Fields
ROWS.subheading: The address information you provide will be used for verifying your identity and personalizing your experience on our platform. We ensure the confidentiality and security of your address details in compliance with our privacy policy.
